{
  "texts": [
    "Case studies are provided in Appendix B and further ablation studies in Appendix D.",
    "We introduce GNN-RAG, a novel graph neural method for enhancing RAG in KGQA with GNNs.",
    "Our contributions are the following.",
    "(1) Framework: GNN-RAG tailors GNNs for KG retrieval due to their ability to handle complex graph information.",
    "(2) Effectiveness: GNN-RAG achieves superior performance when multi-hop information is needed for KGQA."
  ]
}